headline: Is The Cooper Companies Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Even though The Cooper Companies has underperformed the broader Nasdaq Composite over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From CooperCompanies’s Q3 Earnings Call
